@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_esbwsk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp))
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.98 - v1 + 0.37) * (v0 + 0.46 / v0 + 0.06)) - tmp)
    v0 = wp.sin((v0 / (v0 + 0.23 + v2 + 0.31)))
    data[tid] = v0
